                EIDORDEM FOR ZSDT0001OV-NR_ORDEM_VENDA NO-EXTENSION NO INTERVALS,
                EIDMATNR FOR ZSDT0001OV_ALGODAO-MATNR NO-EXTENSION NO INTERVALS.

SELECTION-SCREEN SKIP.

SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF LINE.
PARAMETERS: CK_ST RADIOBUTTON GROUP RAD2.
SELECTION-SCREEN COMMENT 02(50) TEXT-001 FOR FIELD CK_ST.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF LINE.

SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF LINE.
PARAMETERS: CK_ST_A RADIOBUTTON GROUP RAD2.
SELECTION-SCREEN COMMENT 02(50) TEXT-002 FOR FIELD CK_ST_A.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF LINE.

SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF LINE.
PARAMETERS: CK_ST_L RADIOBUTTON GROUP RAD2 DEFAULT 'X'.
SELECTION-SCREEN COMMENT 02(50) TEXT-003 FOR FIELD CK_ST_L.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF LINE.

SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF LINE.
PARAMETERS: CK_ST_D RADIOBUTTON GROUP RAD2.
SELECTION-SCREEN COMMENT 02(50) TEXT-004 FOR FIELD CK_ST_D.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF LINE.

SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF LINE.
