SELECTION-SCREEN COMMENT 02(50) TEXT-005 FOR FIELD CK_ST_R.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF LINE.

SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF LINE.
PARAMETERS: CK_ST_P RADIOBUTTON GROUP RAD2.
SELECTION-SCREEN COMMENT 02(50) TEXT-006 FOR FIELD CK_ST_P.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF LINE.

SELECTION-SCREEN END OF SCREEN 0101.

AT SELECTION-SCREEN OUTPUT.

  DATA: POS TYPE I.

  LOOP AT SCREEN.
    IF SCREEN-NAME EQ 'EVSTEL-LOW' OR SCREEN-NAME EQ 'ECHARG-LOW'.
      SCREEN-INPUT = 0.
      MODIFY SCREEN.
    ENDIF.
  ENDLOOP.

  SET CURSOR FIELD 'EDSINSTR-LOW' OFFSET POS.
